  "title": "Classic Faithful 32x Jappa",
  "description": "A double resolution texture pack that continues Vattic's classic faithful style today.",
  "body": "<center>\n\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/wordmarks/outlined/cracked/cf32j_wordmark.png\">\n\t<h1>A double resolution texture pack that continues Vattic’s classic faithful style today.</h1>\n</center>\n<p>\n\tCreated as a response to Faithful's changing art style, Classic Faithful 32x aims to preserve and restore Vattic's original “painted” art in its full glory. \n\tMost importantly, it also keeps the pack updated, remaking new textures to match the classic style as well.  \n\t<br><br>\n\tThe Jappa version of Classic Faithful 32x is based on the new, updated Minecraft textures that were introduced in release 1.14, re-interpreted as if Vattic was there to make them himself. \n\tGreat care has been taken to emulate Vattic's art style as closely as possible.\n\t<br><br>\n\tIf you've been using Faithful since the old days but prefer the modern look of the new Minecraft textures, you're going to like this pack!\n\n</p>\n<center>\n\t<a href=\"https://discord.gg/KSEhCVtg4J\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/discord_button.png\" alt=\"Discord Server\">\n\t</a>\n  <br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://faithfulpack.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/website_button.png\" alt=\"Website\">\n\t</a>\n</center>\n<hr>\n<center><h2>Additional Information:</h2></center>\n<p>\n\tIf you have any feedback, want to report a bug, or generally need help,\n\tjoin our <a href=\"https://discord.gg/sN9YRQbBv7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Discord</a> server above, make a\n\t<a href=\"https://github.com/ClassicFaithful/32x-Jappa/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub issue</a>,\n\tor comment below. For any commercial or distribution-related questions, refer to our\n\t<a href=\"http://faithfulpack.net/license\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">license</a>.\n\t<br><br>\n\tAll textures and add-ons are provided by contributors volunteering in their free time.\n\tAnyone can submit textures through our Discord server linked above, or make an\n\t<a href=\"http://faithfulpack.net/addons\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">add-on</a>\n\tto officially list on our website. Before you begin, make sure to read our\n\t<a href=\"https://docs.faithfulpack.net/pages/textures/cf32-texturing-guidelines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">texturing guidelines</a>\n\twhich precisely outline the art style of the pack.\n\t<br><br>\n\tEach pack has listings on our <a href=\"faithfulpack.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">website</a>,\n\t<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/faithful_resource_pack/projects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CurseForge</a>,\n\t<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/faithful_resource_pack/submissions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Planet Minecraft</a>,\n\tand <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Faithful-Resource-Pack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Modrinth</a>,\n\tand some packs are additionally listed on <a href=\"https://mcpedl.com/user/faithful-resource-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MCPEDL</a>\n\tand the <a href=\"https://www.minecraftforum.net/members/Faithful_Resource_Pack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Minecraft Forums</a>.\n\t<strong>Downloads from any other sites are unofficial, unsupported and could be dangerous!</strong>\n\tRemember to stay safe on the internet.\n</p>\n<hr>\n<center><h2>Our Other Projects:</h2></center>\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/faithful-32x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/f32_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Faithful 32x\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n\t<br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/faithful-64x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/f64_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Faithful 64x\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n    <br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/classic-faithful-32x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/cf32_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Classic Faithful 32x\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n\t<br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/classic-faithful-64x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/cf64j_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Classic Faithful 64x Jappa\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n</div>",
